Although spelling errors on Old Judge cards are not unprecedented, spelling errors on the names of future HOFers is unusual. Offered is a rare “Jim” Keefe (his parents named the future HOFer Tim) Old Judge card. One of only a few known examples this card is graded a 2 by PSA. Offered at $750. Please email me at [url]oldjudge@gmail.com[/url] if interested or for better images.

Thanks—Jay
